snippet.title: LUCIA and the Possessed World | DevLog 01 | Third-Person Shooter Video Game
snippet.description:
#LuciaAndThePossessedWorld 
The Latina fighting Satina in Hell!
Fight through hell to save your parents on Earth...

Development Log 01:
Menus, Locomotion (Movement), Enemies, A.I., Health, Stamina, Weapons, Pickups and Gore. 

The first game from #BYTESIZEDgames and @MrKylePopovich 
#7DayGameLaunch #DavidWhele #GameDevUnlocked  @DavidWehleGames  #unrealengine 

Wishlist Lucia and the Possessed World on Steam soon!
